commit.message: Changed the logo and the favicon
Added more responsiveness for small devices
Added simple responsiveness to the index page
Removed the login page and made the navbar bigger on the upload page
Added placeholder to preserve file structure of the project
Moved dotenv from dev dependencies to prod dependencies
Added the ability to upload files and push to Dropbox
Added some content to each of the pages
Added basic framework of the application with navbar and logo
